flowchart TD

%% CLIENT
A[React Frontend - TypeScript] -->|Socket.IO| B[API Gateway / NestJS Backend]

%% SOCKET LAYER
B --> C[Socket.IO Gateway]

%% GAME LOGIC
C --> D[Game Service]
D --> E[Room Manager]
D --> F[Drawing Engine]
D --> G[Word Engine]
D --> H[Score Engine]
D --> I[Hint Engine]
D --> J[Timer Engine]

%% REDIS LAYER
E --> R1[(Redis - Room State)]
F --> R2[(Redis - Strokes)]
G --> R3[(Redis - Current Word)]
H --> R4[(Redis - Scores)]
I --> R5[(Redis - Revealed Letters)]

%% PUB/SUB (SCALING)
B <-->|Socket.IO Redis Adapter| R6[(Redis Pub/Sub)]

%% CLIENT UPDATES
C -->|events| A
